title: The Avengers TPB+HC+GN Collection (1967-2013|Dgtl+S|Emp+DCP)
description: This is a collection of several Avengers Trade Paperbacks, Hardcovers and Graphic Novels, as well as some bonus material that covers their history. I have dated each TPB+ with the dates it roughly takes place in order to make it easier for you to read in a coherent manner, and without me having to list ever issue that each trade covers. For a list of included material, please click on "Files" link on the top left-hand corner under the name of the torrent. Thanks to STFMaryville for originally uploading some of this material, as well as the various DCP scanners (especially Bchry-DCP) and Zone-Empire for their digital copies. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
